"Home!" was the reply, in a tone of deep and hopeless despondency,—"Home, to my
                  poor old mother. I've supported her by my wages ever since I've been hired out;
                  that's the reason I haven't laid up any. God knows——"

"You are very good," said Ildegerte, one night, when she was left alone with Judy;
                  and, forgetting that she was in a free state, she added, "To whom do you
                  belong?"
